      <title>奈杰尔·法拉奇每月薪酬近 98,000 英镑 GB News</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-16/nigel-farage-paid-almost-98-000-a-month-to-present-gb-news</link>
