    <item>
      <title>印尼庆祝新首都落成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/indonesia-celebrates-nusantara-a-new-capital-struggling-to-take-shape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚将在婆罗洲岛偏远丛林中建造尚未完工的未来首都，但资金困难、错过最后期限以及国家领导层的变动给这个耗资数十亿美元的项目带来了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/indonesia-celebrates-nusantara-a-new-capital-struggling-to-take-shape</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMLO 盟友开始推动批准其梦寐以求的司法改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/amlo-allies-kick-off-their-push-to-approve-his-coveted-judicial-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的执政联盟议员周五向国会提交的改革计划，墨西哥司法选举将于 2025 年开始，正式启动批准这项备受争议的改革的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/amlo-allies-kick-off-their-push-to-approve-his-coveted-judicial-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 21:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森在打击无家可归者后继续严厉打击犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/newsom-extends-get-tough-push-to-crime-after-homeless-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆签署了一系列反犯罪法案，表明在呼吁严厉打击无家可归者营地三周后，加州将对零售盗窃和汽车盗窃采取更严厉的手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/newsom-extends-get-tough-push-to-crime-after-homeless-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 20:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
